### Use active voice

```jsx
<div>
  <h4 className="typography-body-10 text-muted mb-3">FOR EXAMPLE:</h4>
  <p className="typography-body-10 mb-2 ml-4">
    <span className="text-success font-bold">Do:</span> We’re investigating the issue
  </p>
  <p className="typography-body-10 ml-4">
    <span className="text-danger font-bold">Don't:</span> The problem is being investigated
  </p>
</div>
```

An exception to this is where we’ll end up blaming the customer.

```jsx
<div>
  <h4 className="typography-body-10 text-muted mb-3">FOR EXAMPLE:</h4>
  <p className="typography-body-10 mb-2 ml-4">
    <span className="text-success font-bold">Do:</span> The password is incorrect
  </p>
  <p className="typography-body-10 ml-4">
    <span className="text-danger font-bold">Don't:</span> You’ve entered an incorrect password
  </p>
</div>
```

