### Ensure consistency

Be consistent in the use of a term or the way of expressing information throughout a customer journey.

```jsx
<div>
  <h4 className="typography-body-10 text-muted mb-3">FOR EXAMPLE:</h4>
  <p className="typography-body-10 ml-4">
    <span className="text-danger font-bold">Don't:</span> Using ‘sign in’ and ‘log on’ interchangeably for the same
    brand.
  </p>
</div>
```

Refer to our brand terminology for more information.

